lead_paragraph: New South Wales Waratahs' Michael Hooper scored a try two minutes from time to snatch a 32-30 win over South Africa’s Stormers in a Super Rugby clash at Newlands on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Hooper’s Late Show for Waratahs Sinks Stormers
